Title: Konad Hologram 3D Sticker(KH3D - 5)
Description: Hands and fingernails are considered important points of beauty. Give yours that much needed makeover by adding a touch of elegance to your next do-it-yourself manicure. Let the Konad Hologram 3D Sticker show you how easy it is. Opt for the conventional French manicure and gently stick on these readily adhesive nail art stickers to transform those nails into a work of exotic art. Or use a bold base colour and jazz up the look with these shiny stickers in a delicate floral theme. Either way, you have gone from being plain Jane to fashionista in a matter of minutes. What’s more, these long lasting stickers are easy to use and can be used by women of all ages. The next time you are doing your nails at home, make sure to let your daughter in on all the fun and bond with her. The strong adhesive content of this sticker allows you to breathe easy and multitask as opposed to constantly having to look out for those painstakingly manicured nails. Directions for Use Apply a neat coat of base colour on your freshly clean nails Allow your nails to dry and check if they have completely dried, before using the Konad Kit Take the desired sticker and place it strategically on your painted nails Press it down firmly and get set to dazzle the world.
